<Link id="l00472" /><CodeLine lineNumber="472"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">void</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> advanceData() &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00473" /><CodeLine lineNumber="473"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// &#96;CountersDelta&#96; is a constant zero when using debug info correlation.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00474" /><CodeLine lineNumber="474"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (!Correlator &amp;&amp; !BIDFetcherCorrelator) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00475" /><CodeLine lineNumber="475"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The initial CountersDelta is the in-memory address difference between</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00476" /><CodeLine lineNumber="476"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// the data and counts sections:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00477" /><CodeLine lineNumber="477"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// start(&#95;&#95;llvm&#95;prf&#95;cnts) - start(&#95;&#95;llvm&#95;prf&#95;data)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00478" /><CodeLine lineNumber="478"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// As we advance to the next record, we maintain the correct CountersDelta</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00479" /><CodeLine lineNumber="479"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// with respect to the next record.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00480" /><CodeLine lineNumber="480"><span class="doxyHighlight">      CountersDelta -= </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">sizeof</span><span class="doxyHighlight">(&#42;Data);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00481" /><CodeLine lineNumber="481"><span class="doxyHighlight">      BitmapDelta -= </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">sizeof</span><span class="doxyHighlight">(&#42;Data);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00482" /><CodeLine lineNumber="482"><span class="doxyHighlight">    &#125;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00483" /><CodeLine lineNumber="483"><span class="doxyHighlight">    Data++;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00484" /><CodeLine lineNumber="484"><span class="doxyHighlight">    ValueDataStart += CurValueDataSize;</span></CodeLine>
